# Archon-DataHub — environment configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in. Everything is OPTIONAL: with no credentials the agent
# runs fully offline against deterministic Fakes (Fake DataHub MCP + Fake LLM), so
# `npm test` and the demo scripts are green with zero secrets and zero spend.

# ── DataHub connection (the metadata platform we govern) ──────────────────────
# GMS endpoint of a running DataHub instance (OSS: `datahub docker quickstart`),
# on a CLOUD VM (the stack is ~14 containers — don't run it on a laptop).
DATAHUB_GMS_URL=http://<cloud-vm>:8080
# Personal Access Token — DataHub UI → Settings → Access Tokens.
DATAHUB_GMS_TOKEN=
#
# TRANSPORT — pick one:
#  (a) stdio (default, the reliable OSS path): leave DATAHUB_MCP_URL unset. The
#      live adapter spawns the official server `uvx mcp-server-datahub@latest`
#      with DATAHUB_GMS_URL/TOKEN in its env. Requires `uv` on the host.
#      Override the launcher if needed:
# DATAHUB_MCP_COMMAND=uvx
# DATAHUB_MCP_ARGS=mcp-server-datahub@latest
#  (b) HTTP (Streamable): set DATAHUB_MCP_URL to a hosted MCP endpoint (a DataHub
#      Cloud tenant integrations URL, or a GMS that exposes /mcp).
# DATAHUB_MCP_URL=https://<tenant>.acryl.io/integrations/ai/mcp/
#
# With NEITHER DATAHUB_GMS_URL nor DATAHUB_MCP_URL set → the agent uses the
# built-in Fake DataHub MCP client (fully offline).

# ── LLM (model-agnostic; used by the narrator + optional ReAct loop) ──────────
# The narrator talks to any provider over ONE OpenAI-compatible seam. Set exactly
# one of the keys below; the base URL + default model are auto-selected. With NONE
# set → deterministic Fake LLM (offline, zero spend). Precedence, highest first:
#   1. LLM_API_KEY   — generic override; honors LLM_BASE_URL / LLM_MODEL.
#   2. DASHSCOPE_API_KEY — Qwen via Alibaba Model Studio (qwen-plus).
#   3. GEMINI_API_KEY    — Google Gemini OpenAI-compat (gemini-2.5-flash).
#   4. OPENAI_API_KEY    — OpenAI (gpt-4o-mini).
#   5. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY — Anthropic OpenAI-compat endpoint (claude-opus-4-8).
LLM_API_KEY=
LLM_BASE_URL=
LLM_MODEL=
DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=
GEMINI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
LLM_EMBED_MODEL=text-embedding-v4

# ── pgvector memory (optional RAG grounding store) ────────────────────────────
# Absent → in-memory store (offline). Set to a pgvector-enabled PostgreSQL for
# persistent, cross-session grounding of audit findings.
DATABASE_URL=
